
What is Cloudformation?

    - Cloud formations is AWS answer to IAC (Infrastructure as code)
            - Cloud formation consists of "Stacks"
    
    - Allows you to turn your infrastructure into code and allows you to make large rollout much easier&faster
            - Can declare things such as :
                - Passwords
                - EC2 Instance Types
                - Services
                - Databases
                - etc.

    - Allows you to automate your entire infrastructure

    - Cloudformation templates be written in JSON or YAML formating.
